creator: BuildingLink.com, LLC
descriptionHtml:
The Grange Residents’ App provides all your daily needs in one location.
With the app, you can:

• Log and review maintenance requests
• Receive notifications from concierge regarding upcoming events at The Grange
• Send messages to the onsite management and concierge teams
• View building announcements
• View property appliance manuals and user guides
• View your tenancy details
• Receive offers and discounts from shops and restaurants in your local area
descriptionShort: The Grange Residents’ App onsite services & amenities app
